---
const pills = [
  "EU AI Act · August 2026",
  "Fixed fee · Not day-rate",
  "EU-hosted infrastructure"
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-start mb-12">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-teal flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-navy text-2xl font-bold font-ui">LJ</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-white">Lar Judge</h3>
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-teal border border-teal/40 rounded-full px-3 py-0.5">What If Now</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-light text-sm mb-1">Founder</p>
          <p class="text-slate-light leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Former enterprise ops lead. Spent a decade automating workflows at scale before building What If Now to bring the same rigour — minus the Big Four invoice — to Irish SMEs and charities.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-slate-light leading-relaxed mb-12">
        <p>
          What If Now was founded on a simple belief: your best people shouldn't be spending their week on things that don't need them.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {pills.map((pill) => (
          <span class="bg-navy-light px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-mono text-teal">
            {pill}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
